<Review ID>7939757
<Product Name>Creative ZEN Stone Plus 2 GB Red
<Title>This is sooo cool!
<Date>Sat Oct 27 00:00:00 CST 2007
<Content>I love this little guy!  I had an ipod shuffle that just quit one day.  I was so angry because I had saved all the songs that I really loved on that little thing.  But I had given my boyfriend a Zen mp3 player and he really liked it, so I bought this Zen Stone!  It is so easy to use and upload songs...even the ones I thought I had lost with the ipod.  I have the cassette tape adapter (I had bought for the ipod) for my car and it works with my player and his, too.  I also have some little speakers (also purchased for the ipod) that work with the new Zen players.  I love this Stone...and I got the key chain cover forit.  That is a must since there is not a clip on the body of the player.  It clips onto my key chain and I can take it to class, or in the car, or where ever. AND It picks up radio stations!!!  I can also record leectures in classes.  This is a great little thing and I would highly reccomend it!  
